premise_source_doc_sentence: Béla Ferenc Dezső Blaskó  (  -LSB- ˈbeːlɒ ˈfɛrɛnt͡s ˈdɛʒøː ˈblɒʃkoː -RSB- ; 20 October 1882 -- 16 August 1956  )  , better known as Bela Lugosi  (  -LSB- ləˈgoʊsi -RSB- -LSB- ˈlugoʃi -RSB-  )  , was a Hungarian-American actor , famous for portraying Count Dracula in the 1931 film and for his roles in various other horror films .
